### INSERT / UPDATE / DELETE — executeUpdateQuery()

Returns the number of affected rows:

```java title="UpdateQuery.java"
SHAFT.DB db = new SHAFT.DB(
 DatabaseActions.DatabaseType.POSTGRES_SQL,
